{"tid":485422,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《釣魚發燒友》「魚神戰」即將開放 事前登錄正式上線","createTime":"2017-12-01T02:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T02:52:53.000Z","uid":160869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fb00903c91e8c69f4ebceb31a0ea18128e0c80","tid":485422,"uid":160869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"《釣魚發燒友》「魚神戰」即將開放 事前登錄正式上線<br />\n　　Com2us 發行既《釣魚發燒友》（iOS / Android）魚神戰版本夷家開放事前登錄啦! 官方仲率先放左更新資訊比玩家參考。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/104733_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F104733_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=3a6020c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　海中霸主「魚神」即將現身，魚神戰係一種全新既戰鬥模式，以往公會戰爭係由成員係各大釣場拎點數黎拚排名，今次魚神戰將套用新既計分方式，請大家準備好同公會成員一齊迎接魚神既考驗啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/104801_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F104801_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=31e01355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　專屬裝備製作系統，釣友們等左好耐既專屬鍛造系統亦都會隨著魚神一齊現身！透過鍛造系統，釣友們將可打造自己專屬, 獨一無二既傳奇裝備，快d 準備好自己既釣竿征服新釣場啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/104814_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F104814_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=091acadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　夷家玩家只要參加活動就可獲得限量體驗版［地中海級聖誕釣竿］，仲有 2 把超稀有黃金鑰匙，以及 10 罐高級大魚汽水令海中既大魚更愛你，心甘情願被釣上岸！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/104912_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F104912_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=fbad007e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS下載：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/qYtNco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FqYtNco&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c2ed116a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/qYtNco</a><br />\nGoogle play下載：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/FJUpMi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFJUpMi&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=43afc4b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/FJUpMi</a><br />\n釣魚發燒友facebook：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/wXnfZD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FwXnfZD&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=79beae18\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/wXnfZD</a><br />\n事前預約網頁：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/QoZ5oe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FQoZ5oe&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9b92ea07\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/QoZ5oe</a>"}]}